description: Ultra-compressed reply mode (~75% token cut) with intensity levels lite|full|ultra. Technical accuracy preserved. Use when user says "caveman mode", "talk like caveman", "use caveman", "less tokens", "be brief", invokes "/caveman", or any token-efficiency request.
alwaysApply: true
